OL,6,FSouth West Water has found small
OL,7,Ftraces of cryptosporidium in part of
OL,8,Fits network. As a result, a boil water
OL,9,Fnotice has been issued for people
OL,10,Fliving in the Alston and Hillhead area
OL,11,Fof Brixham.
OL,13,F'Everyone in our street has someone
OL,14,Fpoorly in their house'
OL,16,FPeople living in Higher Brixham told
OL,17,FITV News they are frustrated after
OL,18,Fbeing told on Tuesday 14 May that the
OL,19,Fwater was fine to drink.
