OL,6,F"I'm disgusted really," one woman
OL,7,Fsaid. "Everyone in our street has
OL,8,Fsomeone poorly in their household."
OL,10,FAdvice to residents
OL,12,FWater is safe for washing, bathing and
OL,13,Fflushing the toilet as normal. Boiled
OL,14,Fwater can be stored in a covered
OL,15,Fcontainer in the fridge for 24 hours.
